heading: 1. (1) These Regulations may be cited as the European Union (Novel Foods)
text_raw:
1. (1) These Regulations may be cited as the European Union (Novel Foods) 

(Amendment) (No. 2) Regulations 2025. 

(2) The Principal Regulations, the European Union (Novel Foods) 
(Amendment) Regulations 2024 (S.I. No. 159 of 2024), the Regulations of 2025 
and these Regulations may be cited together as the European Union (Novel 
Foods) Regulations 2022 to 2025.

EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

These Regulations give further effect to Commission Implementing Regulation 
(EU) 2017/2470 of 20 December 2017 which establishes the Union List of Novel 
Foods as amended by the Commission Implementing Regulations specified in 
the Schedule to these Regulations. 

These Regulations may be cited as the European Union (Novel Foods) 
(Amendment) (No. 2) Regulations 2025. 

These Regulations amend the European Union (Novel Foods) Regulations 2022 
(S.I. No. 253 of 2022) in the manner specified in these Regulations and can be 
cited together with all previous amending instruments as the European Union 
(Novel Foods) Regulations 2022 to 2025.
